  <WeaponName>k__BackingField: Rifle
  <WeaponDescription>k__BackingField: "A compact sidearm engineered for reliability
    in hostile environments.\nIts reinforced barrel channels excess heat outward,
    stabilizing recoil across rapid shots.\nFavored by scavengers and operatives
    alike, it\u2019s less about raw power and more about putting the first bullet
    exactly where it matters."
